Link: https://lore.kernel.org/20250225182054.815536219@goodmis.org
Fixes: ef378c3b82338 ("scripts/sorttable: Zero out weak functions in mcount_loc table")
Tested-by: Nathan Chancellor <nathan@kernel.org>
